{"tid":1277946,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"(香港) 六宗教領袖籲政府及不同意見人士放下執著溝通","createTime":"2019-07-02T10:23:15.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-02T10:36:25.000Z","uid":134071,"like":2,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"8cd5ac7ece1f69ea4205968f3a7f5e67a5769492","tid":1277946,"uid":134071,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-02T10:23:15.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"http://www.881903.com/Page/ZH-TW/newsdetail.aspx?ItemId=1128233&amp;csid=261_341\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.881903.com%2FPage%2FZH-TW%2Fnewsdetail.aspx%3FItemId%3D1128233%26csid%3D261_341&d=Mrz8gheyF4cbCiJyPb%2FME08L9AbO9EvXEPTzVQ1jYSs%3D&h=6fc854f8\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://www.881903.com/Page/ZH-TW/newsdetail.aspx?ItemId=1128233&amp;csid=261_341</a><br />\n<br />\n六宗教領袖籲政府及不同意見人士放下執著溝通<br />\n02.07.2019 14:10<br />\n<br />\n本港佛教、天主教、孔教、伊斯蘭教、基督教及道教的領袖，聯合發表聲明，對示威者破壞立法會大樓，深感痛心，呼籲香港市民抵制任何破壞法紀、損及和平及暴力傷害他人的行為，並呼籲所有人應以克己、理性、和平的手法表達意見。六位宗教領袖又呼籲政府、持不同立場及意見的人士，應放下執著，慎思自己的觀點，聆聽他人的聲音，盡快建立有效的溝通渠道，並以真誠的態度開展溝通。<br />\n<br />\n聲明強調，任何訴求不應與港人的福祉相違背，執著己見和對立只會令社會撕裂，無助解決目前困局，又希望社會慎思淨慮，秉著開放、明智、包容及尊重的心，在溝通理解，顧己及人、尊重小我、共建大同的基礎上重新出發，同謀香港大眾的福祉，令香港重回和平共融的軌道。"},{"pid":"64d4cb63b0dada910357e0a38ed0210d8f9e7e8b","tid":1277946,"uid":25468,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-02T10:25:14.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://cdn.thestandnews.com/media/photos/cache/six-13_3J3xO_1200x0.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thestandnews.com%2Fmedia%2Fphotos%2Fcache%2Fsix-13_3J3xO_1200x0.png&h=9ab49776&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"6fe1c57512b9e8b723dd0f49d15ee78fd9d434c8","tid":1277946,"uid":53612,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-02T10:32:15.000Z","msg":"We connect"},{"pid":"f621867ca6b523de7962f67f5ef19980dcdaba2f","tid":1277946,"uid":24295,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-02T10:36:25.000Z","msg":"嘩 林鄭老母勁到"}]}